oofem.out
2D notched beam, midspan notch deleted via #@notch ... delete (Stage 7)
StaticStructural nsteps 1 nmodules 1 solverType "calm" rtolf 1.e-5 maxiter 10 steplength 1.e-5 minsteplength 1.e-5 hpcmode 2 hpc 2 2 1 hpcw 1 1.
errorcheck
domain 2dLattice
OutputManager tstep_all dofman_output { #@CTL1 #@CTL2 #@CTL3 }
ncrosssect 1 nmat 1 nbc 3 nic 0 nltf 1 nset 3
latticecs 1 material 1
latticedamage 1 d 0 talpha 0. e 30.e9 e0 100.e-6 wf 100.e-4 coh 2. ec 10. stype 1
BoundaryCondition 1 loadTimeFunction 1 dofs 3 1 2 6 values 3 0. 0. 0. set 1
BoundaryCondition 2 loadTimeFunction 1 dofs 3 1 2 6 values 3 0. 0. 0. set 2
BoundaryCondition 3 loadTimeFunction 1 dofs 3 1 2 6 values 3 0. -1.e-4 0. set 3
ConstantFunction 1 f(t) 1.
Set 1 nodes 1 #@CTL1
Set 2 nodes 1 #@CTL2
Set 3 nodes 1 #@CTL3
#@grid 2dSM
#@mesher qhull
#@diam 0.004
#@perflag 2 0 0
#@thickness 1.0
#@rect 1 box 4 0. 0. 0.10 0.05
#@notch 1 box 4 0.046 0.0 0.054 0.025 delete
#@controlvertex 1 coords 2 0.005 0.0
#@controlvertex 2 coords 2 0.095 0.0
#@controlvertex 3 coords 2 0.05  0.05
